Springer’s **Rights and Permissions team** is responsible for handling customers’ licensing and permissions needs. On the “Contacts for Rights and Permissions” page you can reach the appropriate contacts:

- **General permission to reuse content (books)**: bookpermissions@springernature.com
- **Journal permissions**: journalpermissions@springernature.com
- **Translation rights for entire books**: booktranslations@springernature.com
- **Paperback and audio rights**: booktranslations@springernature.com
- **Reprints**: reprintwarehouse@springernature.com
- **Reprints for publicity**: press@springernature.com
- **Anti‑piracy queries**: anti-piracy@springernature.com
- **Third‑party distribution queries**: tpd@springernature.com

These contacts are part of the Rights and Permissions department, which takes care of all licensing and permission requests for Springer publications.


